# Optional server-side overrides only. Copy to `.env` if you use them. Never commit `.env`.

# Optional: OpenAI-compatible base URL (e.g. LiteLLM proxy) for requests that
# include a user-supplied API key from the app UI.
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4000

# Optional: override the model used for UI generation (default in route.ts).
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5.2
